      <p class="section__eyebrow">Illinois tax realities we build into your books</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">Three Illinois facts that change how your books are kept.</h2><p class="section__lede">Illinois layers an entity-level tax and Chicago-specific taxes on top of the basics &mdash; these three shape the chart of accounts and the sales-tax setup from day one.</p>
    </header>
